Happy:
I can log in
I can view my shopping cart
I can add, remove, change items in my shopping cart
I can look at items
I can use coupons on my items
I can enter my address for shipping
I can get shipping estimates

Sad:
Incorrect login doesn't work
I can't enter an invalid coupon code
I can't choose items that have run out

Bad:
I can't enter a text value change for items
I can't enter my address with no items
I can't get shipping estimates with no items